msgid "Samādhimhi cute obhāso antaradhāyati dassanañca rūpānaṃ. "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "mn128:19.8"
msgid "Sohaṃ tathā karissāmi yathā me puna na vicikicchā uppajjissati, na amanasikāro, na thinamiddhaṃ, na chambhitattan’ti. (4) "
msgstr "I’ll make sure that neither doubt nor loss of focus nor dullness and drowsiness nor terror will arise in me again.’ "

#. HTML: </p><p>
