msgid "tassa mayhaṃ, anuruddhā, etadahosi: "
msgstr " "

#. VAR: uppilaṃ → ubbillaṃ (bj, pts1) | ubbilaṃ (s1-3, km)
msgctxt "mn128:20.3"
msgid "‘uppilaṃ kho me udapādi, uppilādhikaraṇañca pana me samādhi cavi. "
msgstr "‘Excitement arose in me, and because of that my immersion fell away. "

msgctxt "mn128:20.4"
msgid "Samādhimhi cute obhāso antaradhāyati dassanañca rūpānaṃ. "
msgstr "When immersion falls away, the light and vision of forms vanish. "

msgctxt "mn128:20.5"
msgid "Seyyathāpi, anuruddhā, puriso ekaṃ nidhimukhaṃ gavesanto sakideva pañcanidhimukhāni adhigaccheyya, tassa tatonidānaṃ uppilaṃ uppajjeyya; "
msgstr "Suppose a person was looking for an entrance to a hidden treasure. And all at once they’d come across five entrances! They’d feel excited because of that. "

msgctxt "mn128:20.6"
msgid "evameva kho me, anuruddhā, uppilaṃ udapādi, uppilādhikaraṇañca pana me samādhi cavi. "
msgstr "In the same way, excitement arose in me … "

msgctxt "mn128:20.7"
msgid "Samādhimhi cute obhāso antaradhāyati dassanañca rūpānaṃ. "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "mn128:20.8"
msgid "Sohaṃ tathā karissāmi yathā me puna na vicikicchā uppajjissati, na amanasikāro, na thinamiddhaṃ, na chambhitattaṃ, na uppilan’ti. (5) "
msgstr "I’ll make sure that neither doubt nor loss of focus nor dullness and drowsiness nor terror nor excitement will arise in me again.’ "

